2010-02-13 Ricardo Cruz  <rpmcruz@alunos.dcc.fc.up.pt>

	* src/YGDialog.cc: increased default width by 50 px.

	* src/YGPackageSelectorPluginStub.cc: got rid of the
	flags.

	* src/YGUtils.h/cc: new utilities: compare end of
	two strings, set a pixbuf gray, implement a generic
	callback so to render a separator when an empty row
	is used in a combo-box or a tree-view.

	* src/ygtkrichtext.cc: if "<img src=" is a relative
	path, then use GtkIconTheme. Also added a bgcolor
	attribute to "<font>" for internal use.

	* src/pkg/yzyppwrapper.h/cc: re-wrote our wrapper.
	Makes it easier to integrate crude zypp code.

	* src/pkg/ygtkcellrendererbutton.c &
	ygtkcellrenderersidebutton.c: fixes.

	* src/pkg/YGPackageSelector.cc: bunch of cleanups and
	some UI changes.

	* src/pkg/ygtkpkgdetailview.h/cc, src/pkg/ygtkpkglistview.h/cc,
	src/pkg/ygtkpkgfilterview.h/cc, src/pkg/ygtkpkgundolist.h/cc,
