2009-12-03 Ricardo Cruz  <rpmcruz@alunos.dcc.fc.up.pt>

	* src/YGUtils.cc: proper fix for bug 549943: we
	can't blindly ignore break-lines as white-space.
	How yast2-qt renders HTML is by ignoring white-space
	after a tag has been open (and only on open).

	* src/YGTable.cc & src/YGMenuButton.cc: setLabel()
	not being implemented by a few widgets.
	bug fix: shortcut conflicts were not being revolved.

