2008-12-18  Ricardo Cruz  <rpmcruz@alunos.dcc.fc.up.pt>

	* src/YGSelectionModel.h/cc: bug fix 459313: we are using GTK model
	and YItem tree will mirror each other, which breaks when sorting.
	Replace the algorithm: using a linear search for unique ids now.

	* src/YGTable.cc: sort 1st column by default, and replace the ugly
	"X" by an unicode check mark character.

