	stock icons for warning, error, question and info icons.

	* src/ygtksteps.c: bug fix 432705: first work: use a GtkVBox and labels.

	* src/yzyppwrapper.cc: fixed libzypp deprecated call.

	* src/YGPackageSelector.cc: bug fix: ensure problem solver text is set as
	normal or it may look grayed out.

	* src/YGDialog.cc: bug fix 428965: enable setSize() code.

	* src/ygtkwizard.c: bug fix 432399: dismiss horizontal SizeGroup when
	not enough width is available.

	* src/ygtksteps.h/c: removed unused and unfunctional advance method.

2008-10-06  Ricardo Cruz  <rpmcruz@alunos.dcc.fc.up.pt>

	* src/ygtkwizard.h/.c: collapse all button functions and accept button
	pointers as argument.

	* src/YGUtils.cc: use stock on image -- just test it before -- to
	track status like sensitive.

	* src/ygtkwizard.c: some tools don't set a header, either use "YaST" or
	retain last one set.

	* src/linklabel.c: hide in effect if text empty.

