	* src/ygtkprogressbar.h/c: makes progress bar a bit smoother. Just
	using the last change as guide with some liberal tweaks.

	* src/YGProgressBar.cc (YGProgressBar): use ygtkprogressbar
	* src/YGProgressBar.cc (YGBusyIndicator): use pulse-step to make it
	smoother.
	* src/YGProgressBar.cc (YGDownloadProgress): show download size in
	the progress bar.

2008-09-23  Ricardo Cruz  <rpmcruz@alunos.dcc.fc.up.pt>

	* src/YGWidget.cc: bug fix 421794: clean any emitted event when
	destroyed. The new libyui crashes when doing YWidget::isValid()
	for a destroyed widget due to memory overwrite.

