	Make it align to the left.

	* src/YGLayout.cc: digress last change. Stefan is doing that in libyui now.

2008-09-09  Stanislav Visnovsky  <visnov@novell.com>

	* Version 2.17.0

2008-09-09  Ricardo Cruz  <rpmcruz@alunos.dcc.fc.up.pt>

	* src/yzyppwrapper.cc/.h: added support for Languages. Made Ypp::Package a
	proxy class for Ypp::Package::Impl which is now subclassed into PackageSel,
	for Selectable objects, and PackageLang for locales.
	* src/YGPackageSelector.cc: added Language option.

	* src/yzyppwrapper.cc: fixed Pattern installed status.
	* src/YGPackageSelector.cc: got rid of patterns remove button.

	* src/YGPackageSelector.cc: clear search entry on UI change.
	* src/ygtkfindentry.c: bug fix: not syncing icon properly when entry
	text was deleted by instruction as an insert is triggered.

	* src/YGUI.cc: redirect GTK log messages to libyui system.
	* src/ygtkrichtext.c: enable html parsing warnings that go to libyui.

	* src/yzyppwrapper.cc: fixed repositories query (related to bug 418781).
	Was using some duplicated zypp API that is dysfunctional it seems.
	* src/YGPackageSelector.cc: escaping the URL as some characters (like &)
	were confusing the Pango parser. Use the FILE stock icon for the ISO.

