	(Ypp::PkgListener): translate later when we have the
	textdomain setup correctly.

	* src/YGUI.cc (YGUI::setTextdomain): impl.
	* src/YGi18n.h: add TEXTDOMAIN / dgettext / dngettext
	to the calls.

	* POTFILES: add missing files-to-be-translated.

